{
  "stem": "4189.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the army, the German army was so fast, they were so mobilized, that they overrun these people, and they overrun them before they ever got there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So eventually, they all came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But while these people were away, we opened up a room also on the roof, under the roof, another room that belonged to them which they had rented to a young man, incidentally.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this young man also went away-- also went away to France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he did not come back right away, so we stayed in that room all by ourselves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course it was very difficult for us, because we had no food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no money to buy food, so we actually had to beg for food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then everything got rationed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once the occupation started, they put out ration cards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we ourselves, my brother and myself, we could not get any ration cards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We applied for them but they would not give to us because they said, hey, how can two young children live by themselves?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're-- they're trying to cheat the government, they're trying to get extra cards for their families.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they would not give us a ration cards, and we couldn't even buy the meager rations that they were giving out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were in a very desperate situation there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on top of it, the people that owned the place, the people that we were staying with came back, and they wanted their place back and they throw us, virtually throw us, out in the street because we had no money to pay them.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The joint wasn't there anymore because the joint was sending money from America.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the war was going on, so they couldn't send any more money, so we were on our own.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
